Unocal Corp said it plans to introducetruck lube centers at most of the 148 Unocal 76 Auto/TruckStopsalong the nation's interstate highways.    The company said the centers will be the first nationalprogram to offer over-the-road trucks a convenient and completelube-and-oil-change service. The centers will offer a 20-pointlubrication and oil change at a suggested price of 99.95 dlrsfor most trucks.    Unocal said the price will be the same or lower thancommercial grages and truckstops now charge in most areas. Reuter&#3;